</use></svg></a></div></section><div class='l-widget widget-default widget_text'><div class='widget-header'><h2>Case of the Week</h2></div><div class="textwidget"><p><a href="https://eguide.nl/case/lightyear-companion-app" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> <img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://www.emerce.nl/content/uploads/2023/11/hike-on3.png" width="175px" height="150px" /></a><br /><strong>Lightyear Companion App</strong><br />Lightyear is ontwikkelaar van auto’s op zonne-energie, met als missie het leveren van een superieure gebruikerservaring met minimale impact op het milieu. Voor hun eerste low-volume auto creëerde Hike One op basis van onderzoeksresultaten en herbruikbare componenten een companion app die naadloos aansluit bij de klantbeleving en missie van Lightyear. <a href="https://eguide.nl/case/lightyear-companion-app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bekijk de case op EGUIDE</a></p></div></div><section class="m-container-aside-widgets__section"><div class="m-emerce-training-widget"><h2 class="e-container-title e-container-title--small">Emerce Academy</h2><div class="m-emerce-training-widget__content"><a href="https://www.emerce.nl/academy/trainingen/contentstrategie/" class="m-emerce-training-widget__training" target="_blank"><div class="m-emerce-training-widget__calendar"><span class="m-emerce-training-widget__day">15</span><span class="m-emerce-training-widget__month">Nov</span></div><div class="m-emerce-training-widget__training-details"><h4 class="m-emerce-training-widget__training-name">Contentstrategie</h4><h4 class="m-emerce-training-widget__training-location">Online classroom</h4></div></a><a href="https://www.emerce.nl/academy/trainingen/web3/" class="m-emerce-training-widget__training" target="_blank"><div class="m-emerce-training-widget__calendar"><span class="m-emerce-training-widget__day">16</span><span class="m-emerce-training-widget__month">Nov</span></div><div class="m-emerce-training-widget__training-details"><h4 class="m-emerc